The following free fonts have been used on this project :

- Neuropol X Font for the game title (https://www.1001fonts.com/neuropol-x-free-font.html)
- Galivers Sans Font for the text in the header of the game itself (https://www.1001fonts.com/galiver-sans-font.html)
- Anita Semi-square Font for the text on the buttons and in the help section (https://www.1001fonts.com/anita-semi-square-font.html)

All graphical assets have been made by myself (Grimmys).

This game has been made in collaboration with Jessica Robo, who did an amazing job for the soundtrack and the sound effects.